name: Rossmatterklön
description:
Introduction

Aquatic canyon at the very end of Klöntal.

Approach

From the lake, walk up to Klönstalden, the canyon immediatly starts there.

Descent

A few aquatic rappels, unfortunately not very continuous, and some downclimbs from time to time.

Exit

Not far from the canyon end are houses, from which you can walk on the road.

Red tape

Beta sites

Trip reports and media

Further description in the following book : https://www.canyoning-equipment.com/produkt/swiss-alps-canyoning-vol-2-0/
